extendedInfo.description: Curious about your intelligence rate? Perhaps you simply enjoy a stimulating challenge? We offers two professionally developed and validated IQ assessments to test your mental powers!Best IQ Test program for Android!Examine your brain powers.kw: logiq, iq test, brain test, Mathematical , trivia, general IQ, logical IQ, brain puzzle, intelligence.

reviews.title: Huge bug!!!
reviews.comment: Big problem the circles for the answers cover the answers themselves! Usually it\'s okay but got halfway through to a math answer and wad blank ad all the answers where covered, takes all the fun out of it. If that was fixed then would defiantly be one of the best ones I\'ve played but because of that it\'s now the worst.
reviews.author: Jasmine Macdonald

reviews.title: So so
reviews.comment: Its ok, just not great. It feels like the developers really rushed this app, and I\'d like to see it revamped with less typos amd errors. The IQ test also is a bit inaccurate, as is the EQ test. Has some potential though.

reviews.comment: This was aweful! I would do it and there was just definitions! Theres a lot more to having a high iq than definitions!

reviews.title: Inaccurate and Inadequate
reviews.comment: Many of the questions had a misspelled word in the answer. The result being that you cannot believe that this test is good in any way. Not to mention that the result is a mere score rather than an actual iq number.
